snippet.title: [Quake] January Jump Jam - jjj_smilecythe "Mana Vemputin" Nightmare 100%
snippet.description:
Really nice jam pack this month built around jcr's excellent jump mod. Jump boots are a fun powerup and both this map and mazu's are long adventures that use them very well, reusing the same spaces multiple times in interesting ways. The shorter maps are also all excellent. There's not a dud in the whole set!

I forgot about the mega secret at the rollercoaster, whoops! I also don't really get the rocket launcher secret visible from the map start - you can only escape it with the triple jump boots, as far as I can tell, and once you have those the final arena and attendant rocket launcher are accessible. Maybe I missed something or there's an easier way to rocket jump out of there without banging your head on the way up, not sure!

download here: http://www.celephais.net/board/view_thread.php?id=61832 recorded with quakespasm-spiked etc. etc
